{"tid":1282052,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(TG)抗負能量 我好想組個跑步團同大家改善一下情緒","createTime":"2019-07-03T12:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T08:49:29.000Z","uid":92200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81f5892bdaab5ff3c62604ee3f626557b9247bc7","tid":1282052,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"頭先好似POST錯區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再貼多次<br />\n呢家成個網絡都充斥住負能量，我明白大家都好緊張最近社會嘅事<br />\n但一個人不斷接受同追逐最新資訊，當中又咁多負能量，其實個人情緒會好崩緊<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望大家要平衡一下情緒，起碼每晚都抽少少時間跑步 令到個人舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n但自己跑可能無咩動力，我地幾個社工想組個跑步團比大家，只要大家想跑步都可以喺個組入面搵巴打絲打組隊<br />\n當然，跑步速度技術唔係重點，只想大家輕鬆跑 傾下計 互相支持同鼓勵大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地幾個可以集中返新界西陪大家，其他區我地盡量抽時間陪大家 或者 大家都可以自組<br />\n<br />\n有咩詳情入黎傾下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑步好處<br />\n1. 減壓<br />\n2. 改善情緒問題<br />\n3. 強身健體<br />\n4. 識朋友 (至少有我地)<br />\n<br />\n加入TG Group link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/D8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FD8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c204a43d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/D8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w</a>"},{"pid":"aeea89d39098db57fcf358015e6b88703ed71c3c","tid":1282052,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地會陪你跑架"},{"pid":"da8f564895259882f4702fae1429bee88964e602","tid":1282052,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有人入左黎 開始組隊"},{"pid":"7ad54797d27933055860aa83ac14d0a46e192dd8","tid":1282052,"uid